      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I need to prep a quick briefing for the board meeting tomorrow regarding the NeuroZest Phase II results. They're looking at the budget for next year, so I need a summary that captures the key takeaways and helps justify why we should push forward into Phase III. Can you give me a rundown of how the efficacy data looks?",
